	<title>
		<paragraph x="12" y="+4" width="605" height="0" style="headline" tabs="0" indent="0"><![CDATA[<B><TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="12" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0"><B>Read the paragraph and decide which of the ideas from the brainstorming exercise the writer has included.</B></FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT></B>]]></paragraph>
	</title>
	<body>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+16" width="470" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">The arguments in favour of an international language are both ideological and practical. Firstly, it is sometimes said that linguistic diversity divides people and leads to conflict. In other words, if we removed language differences, we would find it easier to understand each other's point of view and, as a result, co-operate more easily. Secondly, it is argued that if everyone learned the same language, a great deal of time-consuming and expensive translation work would no longer be necessary, and this would be of great benefit to international trade. Finally, it is generally agreed that a common language would make international travel much easier for everyone.</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="450" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="_sans" SIZE="12" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0"> </FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="470" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0"><B>1</B>  Which of these arguments in favour of an international language are included in the paragraph?</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="450" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="_sans" SIZE="12" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0"> </FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="450" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">[1]</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="450" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">[2]</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="450" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">[3]</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="450" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">[4]</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="450" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">[5]</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph type="text" x="12" y="+0" width="450" height="0" style="normal" tabs="" indent="0"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">[6]</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<paragraph height="0" width="605" y="+16" x="12"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT SIZE="2"></FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
		<field id="1" group="1" type="i:target" mode="0">
			<answer correct="true">A  Improve international co-operation and understanding</answer>
		</field>
		<field id="2" group="2" type="i:target" mode="0">
			<answer correct="false">B  Reduce nationalism</answer>
		</field>
		<field id="3" group="3" type="i:target" mode="0">
			<answer correct="true">C  Reduce the amount of translation work needed</answer>
		</field>
		<field id="4" group="4" type="i:target" mode="0">
			<answer correct="true">D  Help international trade</answer>
		</field>
		<field id="5" group="5" type="i:target" mode="0">
			<answer correct="false">E  Simplify electronic communication</answer>
		</field>
		<field id="6" group="6" type="i:target" mode="0">
			<answer correct="true">F  Make international travel easier</answer>
		</field>
